    <step order="1" name="Define IComposeSessionService">Methods: `EnsureSessionForDocumentAsync(documentId, userId, ct)` (returns ChatSession), `RebindToDocumentIdAsync(currentDocumentId, newDocumentId, ct)` (idempotent), `GetSessionAsync(documentId, ct)`. All take CancellationToken.</step>
